          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_8163543532435039070.png",
                "id": "talent88169",
                "key": "忍刀·终末番",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "忍刀·终末番"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，本角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备技能：风风轮舞踢</span>。<br>如果当前技能引发了扩散，则<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">风风轮舞踢</span>将改为造成被扩散元素的伤害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">风风轮舞踢<br></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技<br></span>（需准备1个行动轮）<br>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>（或被扩散元素的伤害）。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/0d49f00d17fc351c654b35e9c3df69a0_787012988907785319.png",
                "id": "talent47770",
                "key": "呜呼流·风隐急进",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "呜呼流·风隐急进"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">风元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">不倒貉貉</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/9810aeb4be1a04544ed8bd2e2fdb4c9f_7285046448401159885.png",
                "id": "talent91644",
                "key": "呜呼流·影貉缭乱",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "呜呼流·影貉缭乱"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，治疗我方受伤最多的角色2点。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8327525523447132859.png",
                "id": "talent28891",
                "key": "不倒貉貉",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/48a8c90a05701c12e7e340501f089bc8_4615027102708012160.png",
                "title": "不倒貉貉"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">扩散（冰）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成<span>1点冰伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">扩散（水）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成<span>1点水伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">扩散（火）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成<span>1点火伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">扩散（雷）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成<span>1点雷伤害</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_5108953233504811424.png",
                "id": "talent88891",
                "key": "风元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "风元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备技能</span></strong></p><p>有些技能无法被直接使用，而是需要一定次数的行动轮来进行<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>。</p><p>轮到一位牌手行动时，如果该牌手的「出战角色」正在<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>技能，则跳过该牌手的行动：如果技能已经完成<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>，角色将会在此时直接使用此技能。（此类需要<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>的技能，无法触发「使用技能后」「角色引发元素反应后」等效果。）</p><p>只有「出战角色」才能<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>技能；如果正在<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>技能的「出战角色」被切换到后台，技能的<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>就会被打断。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: white\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: white\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_2210533953808001199.png",
